Articles.Content:
Updating with the patcher, and again duplicate parts in the list: strut connector and fuel lines.

(this is tagged Support - Windows, but I assume it's cross-platform)

For both, there's new files (changed recently) under /GameData/Squad/Parts/CompoundParts/; there's also old files (file date from the previous update) under /GameData/Squad/Parts/Structural/ (strut connector) and /GameData/Squad/Parts/Utility (fuel line).

I'll delete the old files and see what happens.
Yup. That worked as expected for me.
For me too. It's difficult to say whether I've really got the new ones, but placement behaviour has changed at any rate.
